{"tid":23885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母未能接受兒子販毒自殺亡 青年判囚19年半😔","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T10:06:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"531e5af3e8edccf3d5492ce37bd449f37e84c945","tid":23885,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"24歲無業青年稱為賺錢找卡數，去年12月中擬替毒販將兩隻以冰毒壓製、偽裝成生果盤的毒品製品帶到澳洲，惟於機場辦理登機手續後即被警方截獲。青年早前承認販毒罪，涉及冰毒2.91公斤、市值161萬元，今求情透露母親因接受不了兒子販毒而自殺身亡。法官指事件不幸且令人婉惜，感嘆為人父母都不希望子女會作奸犯科，販毒或加入黑社會。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時指，被告嚴志成沒把握機會及早認罪，無法得到1/3全數刑期減免，加上被告純為錢犯案、案件涉及國際元素，故判被告入獄19年半。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56006548&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56006548%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161205&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=968c513b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56006548%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161205&h=211d4cc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56006548&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161205</a>"},{"pid":"c96298c03107dec3e29693d117fffb6d19508b4a","tid":23885,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"出返黎44歲姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d0b0434c28596538749ad252d913d4a3593972","tid":23885,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"個老母做乜咁傻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988bf602874c1eaa3699ea3a00d958f1adb7318c","tid":23885,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74f9f37455d338aaff13d377f595125